snippet.title: Undertale: Bits and Pieces Together - BNP TOGETHER 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Undertale:Bits and Pieces Together is a mod that allows you to play the 
entire original Undertale Bits and pieces mod but with two players! (3-4p WIP) Mod by me, https://www.youtube.com/@LeoHaha and https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=blacklambcz
The battle system, Fights, Cutscenes, And Sprites, And dialogue (soon enough) have all been modified! to fill the experience with your friends 

(I AM NOT AFFLIRATED WITH THE BNP TEAM AND I DIDNT CREATE BNP ALL RIGHTS GO TO BLAIZE.MAYES AND MR.GEORGE) https://www.youtube.com/@DarthGeorge43
https://www.youtube.com/@blaizemayes8044

#undertale #mods
